  "format": "The 25-for-25 countdown reaches No. 10. Amanda Dobbins makes the case for Sofia Coppola's 'Marie Antoinette' over the more expected 'Lost in Translation,' and she and Sean Fennessey work through the $40 million Versailles shoot, the post-punk soundtrack, and Kirsten Dunst's performance.",
  "segments": [
